---
title: Buy Order Flow
---
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as Browser
  participant F as SessionAuthFilter
  participant T as TradingService
  participant M as MarketDataService
  participant R as Redis
  participant P as PostgreSQL

  U->>F: POST /api/orders (Bearer token)
  F->>R: GET session:token
  R-->>F: userId, email
  Note over F: Rejects with UNAUTHORIZED<br/>before any controller runs
  F->>T: executeOrder(userId, request)

  rect rgb(243, 247, 255)
    Note over T,P: One @Transactional unit
    T->>M: getLatestPrice(symbol)
    M->>R: GET price:BTC
    R-->>M: quote
    Note over T,M: Price read BEFORE the lock,<br/>so nobody waits through a Redis hop
    T->>P: SELECT wallet FOR UPDATE
    Note over P: Any other order for this wallet<br/>now waits here until commit
    P-->>T: wallet (locked)
    T->>T: check funds, MoneyMath.buyQuantity()<br/>rounds DOWN at 8dp
    T->>P: UPDATE wallet balance
    T->>P: UPSERT holding
    T->>P: INSERT transaction
    Note over T,P: All three land, or none do
  end

  T-->>U: OrderResponse (new balance + position)
